1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 16=

3
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:23,160
You're following me?

4
00:00:23,160 --> 00:00:23,960
Hey,

5
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:26,190
isn't this my fiance?

6
00:00:26,550 --> 00:00:28,230
What brings you to the hospital?

7
00:00:28,870 --> 00:00:29,670
Huh?

8
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:33,640
Don't tell me you've got
some embarrassing condition!

9
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:35,560
Stop talking nonsense. Move!

10
00:00:35,710 --> 00:00:38,240
Come on, don't be embarrassed.

11
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:40,280
It's not that embarrassing!

12
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:41,880
Please, I'm begging you!

13
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:42,840
Leave me alone!

14
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:46,840
It's okay!

15
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:51,710
Even if you can't get it up,
I won't look down on you!

16
00:00:56,070 --> 00:00:57,840
(Zechen, I'm overseas now.)

17
00:00:58,390 --> 00:00:59,240
(Everything's fine.)

18
00:01:00,030 --> 00:01:01,320
(Make sure you eat well.)

19
00:01:01,350 --> 00:01:02,520
(Take good care of yourself.)

20
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,120
(Wait for me.)

21
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:13,790
Zemu,

22
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,590
it's almost over.

23
00:01:22,710 --> 00:01:25,280
We're one step away
from taking Jiang Xiao down.

24
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:30,870
We'll be reunited soon.

25
00:01:40,790 --> 00:01:44,430
(Grandpa, please get better soon.)

26
00:01:44,790 --> 00:01:46,040
(The company needs you.)

27
00:01:46,510 --> 00:01:48,640
(Our whole family needs you too.)

28
00:02:00,230 --> 00:02:01,430
These fireworks...

29
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,960
Maybe an electric shock
can separate us again.

30
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,630
Calm down.

31
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:18,120
(These are memories
between Jiang Zechen and me.)

32
00:02:21,910 --> 00:02:24,800
Let's trace it back to the source.

33
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:26,910
Yes, ma'am.

34
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,590
One bowl of noodles.
No cilantro, no spice.

35
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,190
Hey, boss!

36
00:02:31,310 --> 00:02:32,190
Wait!

37
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:35,080
Extra cilantro. Make it crazy spicy!

38
00:02:36,310 --> 00:02:36,960
Huh?

39
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:38,590
Why don't I feel pain?

40
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:39,710
I do!

41
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,560
(So he wasn't lying.)

42
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,800
(Our minds really are linked.)

43
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:56,000
Let's get your body back.

44
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:08,080
(He's done so much for me.)

45
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:22,470
(Jiang Zechen, wait for me!)

46
00:03:22,870 --> 00:03:24,150
(I'm coming to you!)

47
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:31,560
(Zemu,)

48
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,430
(I miss you so much.)

49
00:03:51,310 --> 00:03:52,710
Why is my heart beating so fast?

50
00:03:55,150 --> 00:03:55,960
Qiao Nian.

51
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,750
Zechen,

52
00:03:58,030 --> 00:03:58,960
I remember now!

53
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,800
I remember everything!

54
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:09,710
I remember.

55
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,600
My consciousness...

56
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:20,360
All the memories from
when it was living inside you...

57
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,680
I remember them all.

58
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,120
I love you.

59
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:53,360
Can you say that again?

60
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,000
I didn't hear you.

61
00:04:57,950 --> 00:04:58,750
Say it again.

62
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:04,040
I don't say sweet things twice.

63
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,680
Didn't that backfire on you too?

64
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,270
Did it hurt?

65
00:05:16,310 --> 00:05:17,240
Jiang Zechen,

66
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,560
thank you.

67
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,920
Thank you for always protecting me.

68
00:05:25,870 --> 00:05:27,120
You did so much.

69
00:05:29,390 --> 00:05:30,720
And I knew nothing.

70
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:35,720
Why didn't you ever tell me?

71
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,560
You had lost your memory.

72
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:45,040
Jiang Xiao and Qiao Wenjun
both had their eyes on you.

73
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:48,390
But our minds were no longer linked.

74
00:05:50,270 --> 00:05:52,560
I couldn't stay by your side
and protect you every second.

75
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,160
So...

76
00:05:57,390 --> 00:05:58,430
I had to get

77
00:05:58,430 --> 00:06:00,600
Jiang Xiao and Qiao Wenjun
to keep each other in check.

78
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:06,000
So that day at the hospital,

79
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:06,870
when I told you to go,

80
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:09,560
you didn't explain anything.

81
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:19,780
♪The sky's waiting for the fog to clear♪

82
00:06:20,540 --> 00:06:23,780
♪Like ears waiting for an answer♪

83
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:29,980
♪Those lost still struggle on♪

84
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,560
This is your punishment.

85
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:42,720
For always giving up too easily.

86
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:45,040
For keeping everything from me.

87
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,360
For deciding what's best
for me on your own.

88
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:50,750
I'm sorry.

89
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,630
From now on, I'll discuss
everything with you.

90
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,360
But...

91
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,430
Can you

92
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:02,800
stop pushing me away?

93
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,510
Promise me.

94
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:09,300
♪I waited through autumn leaves
and winter's decay♪

95
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:12,460
♪Yet never got the chance♪

96
00:07:12,860 --> 00:07:17,340
♪To plant these blooming flowers
with you♪

97
00:07:18,870 --> 00:07:20,600
So now we're back together.

98
00:07:21,660 --> 00:07:25,020
♪I have waited for the moon
to wander and stars to shift and flow♪

99
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:28,070
♪Yet I never waited for nights
with you and a painted world♪

100
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:29,160
Now that Grandpa's stable,

101
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:33,720
my biggest dream is to find my mom.

102
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,270
I'll be by your side.

103
00:07:48,980 --> 00:07:56,020
♪Whose voice keeps climbing
into my dreams?♪

104
00:07:58,190 --> 00:07:59,480
So it's a yes?

105
00:08:00,540 --> 00:08:03,700
♪Time tells me to let go♪

106
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:07,460
♪I waited through spring rain
and summer’s fading heat♪

107
00:08:08,180 --> 00:08:11,340
♪I waited through autumn leaves
and winter's decay♪

108
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:14,580
♪Yet never got the chance♪

109
00:08:14,580 --> 00:08:19,180
♪To plant these blooming flowers
with you♪

110
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:29,970
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

111
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:37,850
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

112
00:08:37,900 --> 00:08:41,690
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

113
00:08:42,210 --> 00:08:45,490
♪Where this ends♪

114
00:08:45,490 --> 00:08:52,770
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

115
00:08:52,770 --> 00:08:57,100
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

116
00:08:57,140 --> 00:09:00,220
♪Love turns into pain♪

117
00:09:00,290 --> 00:09:04,410
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

118
00:09:04,570 --> 00:09:08,050
♪Yet I still want you close♪

119
00:09:08,050 --> 00:09:12,220
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

120
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:15,530
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

121
00:09:15,530 --> 00:09:20,100
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

122
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:26,410
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

123
